10) Create "Cost per claim & YoY by Type" Chart. 17

It was a long process, wasn't it ?  Now you have a good sharp looking dynamic chat.
To build the second chart with the same theme will be a long process again, but it can be easy, if you follow these steps:


STEP 1:  Creating a chart based on the previous Chart.


  1. Copy  and past "Cost per claim & YoY by Month" Chart.   Use Ctrl V  to past  the chart.
  2. Delete the "month" and "weekDayName" From the shared axis 
  3. Drag and drop "Claim type" column to the shared axis 


STEP 2 : Edit the chart's format:

  1. Click on the Format icon
  2. Fix the  Card  Size:     X Position: 669    Y position: 360        Width : 300                  Height: 360
  3. Turn Off  Y axis , to get more space
  4. Fix the Title Change "Cost per claim & YoY by Month" to "Cost per claim & YoY by Type"
  5. You should get a Chart Like this chat bellow.
